{"tid":636176,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"名宿：酋長球場應易名「雲加球場」","createTime":"2018-04-20T15:19:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T19:17:11.000Z","uid":4661,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e45adb5d331ba4bf83ccbb5f52a7702347bbb975","tid":636176,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T15:19:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EqVcPDp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEqVcPDp.jpg&h=bd1636b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=uWPqRSjJFZLVC4jkpPW5s1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=68507cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】兩名阿仙奴名宿麥臣和阿倫史密夫異口同聲表示，對阿仙奴主帥雲加的最佳致敬方法，是將酋長球場改名為「雲加球場」。<br />\n<br />\n雲加宣佈季後離開阿仙奴，於兵工廠執教22年的教練生涯即將告終，有人為此感到可惜，有人則提議如何向該名一代名帥致敬。<br />\n<br />\n曾與雲加傳不和的前阿仙奴中場麥臣（Paul Merson）說：「阿仙奴應放棄阿聯酋航空的贊助，他們根本不需要金錢，接著將主場命名為雲加球場，那是他的球場，球場是由他建造和打造出來的，儘管人們已稱那是『酋長雲加球場』，但他是值得的。」<br />\n<br />\n另一阿仙奴名宿阿倫史密夫（Alan Smith）亦力撐麥臣的說法：「我跟麥臣的說法一致，認為那是一個分妙到毫巔的提議，以其名字為球場命名，是向其致敬的最合適方式，明顯地，球會刻下絕不願意放棄那數以百萬鎊計，來自球場命名權的贊助費，但我認為那是最好不過。」"},{"pid":"d7822fe5911a674760693eb2b7bb823dff7aba65","tid":636176,"uid":19334,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T15:20:27.000Z","msg":"支持!"},{"pid":"8e7bae1bf92318ee9a77ab39da26501817fdbde2","tid":636176,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T15:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a55b338e10bbe9367eb18fa2f2fed2b7ba2cab","tid":636176,"uid":76488,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T15:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd72a8571